The Pan-African News Wire (PANW) has been just started to be part of the struggle against imperialism by providing unfiltered African news through email subscriptions. What we are giving to the world is a website created by Africans for connecting Africans to the world media. It is publishing news from different works of African's writings that cover a rich history of all Africa, especially from the Afro-United Professional Alliance http://www.A-PNA.org covered by Pan-African News Wire with its decline agenda about African's messages to the world.

We publish all events that are representing the struggles which took place in different parts of Africa. As most of our journalists here in Africa are reporting the news from governments, we as amateur journalists are fighting the hidden agenda with an independent Afro-Pan African News Website covering the hidden agenda of the informers as most of the media which speak to us ispires our lives toward the poor African's welfare.

It is happening in between the conflicts generated or enhanced by the imperialist's designs against Africa during the United States Crime Against Humanity in Iraq against the secular idea in the Middle East by its war campaigns against Iran.
